		"name": "Event Management System API",
		"description": "Complete Event Management System API collection for Louco Event backend.\n\n## Base URL\n- Development: http://localhost:8080\n\n## Authentication\nAll endpoints require JWT token in Authorization header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>\n```\n\n## Language Support\nAPI supports Turkish and English. Set Accept-Language header:\n- `tr` for Turkish\n- `en` for English (default)\n\n## Updated Route Structure\n- Address Management: `/api/v1/addresses`\n- Event Management: `/api/v1/events/manage`\n- Ticket Management: `/api/v1/tickets/event/:event_id`\n- Invitation Management: `/api/v1/invitations/event/:event_id`\n- Public Events: `/api/v1/events`\n\n## Event + Address Workflow\n1. Create Address: POST `/api/v1/addresses`\n2. Create Event with address_id: POST `/api/v1/events/manage`\n\n## Response Format\nAll responses follow this standard format:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"i18n.key\",\n  \"data\": {},\n  \"errors\": null\n}\n```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
